# Joo Navigation

Read order:

1. user-provided exact files
2. `rules/context-navigation.md`
3. `AI_INDEX.md`
4. at most one relevant `.ai/indexing/maps/*` shard
5. file-level `@ai-*` headers
6. relevant source files
7. imports from the first relevant source file
8. relevant tests
9. targeted search only if needed

Do not read every map shard.

Report only files read, reason, next target, and uncertainty.
